data.description: Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity! An updated 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in a prime location. This property offers a comfortable and modern living space, perfect for families or individuals looking for a cozy sanctuary. One of the highlights of this home is the nice size backyard, providing ample space for outdoor activities and relaxation. Whether you enjoy gardening, hosting barbecues, or simply lounging under the sun, this backyard has it all. Plus, you'll love the convenience of the covered patio, offering lots of shade. Located in a prime location, you'll have easy access to amenities like schools, shopping centers, parks, and more. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a home that ticks all the boxes!
